title: Eventbrite Demo Event-Tri The Beach
desc: Eventbrite offers an effective race registration solution to maximize participation and reach for your endurance events?both large and small. We offer customizable features, and powerful marketing and social media tools to help acquire new athletes, volunteers and fans. Race organizers can also benefit from anytime access to valuable sales and registration reports, and use of our mobile registration solutions for seamless onsite check-in and race entry.
